# Data Table

## Anatomy

- table container
- header row
- sortable header cell
- body row
- cell
- row actions
- pagination
- empty state
- loading skeleton

## States

- loading
- empty
- populated
- sorted
- filtered
- selected rows
- error

## Variants

- dense
- comfortable
- selectable
- with sticky header
- with row actions

## Tokens

- `--color-border`
- `--color-muted`
- `--color-background`
- `--space-*`
- `--text-sm`

## Accessibility

- Use semantic `<table>` when data is tabular.
- Sort buttons announce direction.
- Row selection uses checkbox semantics.
- Pagination is keyboard reachable and labelled.
